      • DataFrame

        public DataFrame()

      • DataFrame

        public DataFrame​(File csv)
          throws FileNotFoundException,
                 ColumnSizeMismatch
        Creates a DataFrame from a CSV file. Note that we not yet handle CSV File with escape character " (quotation mark), and then we not handle CSV file which contain , (comma) in cells. Note that columns name will be "column" + column index by default.
        Parameters:
        csv - CSV file to read.
        Throws:
        FileNotFoundException - If file doesn't exist with specify path
        ColumnSizeMismatch - if CSV file contains different column lengths

      • DataFrame

        public DataFrame​(ArrayList<Object>... arrays)
          throws UnsupportedTypeException,
                 EmptyArrayException,
                 ColumnSizeMismatch
        Creates a new DataFrame and fills its column with given arrays. Note that columns name will be "column"+ column index by default.
        Parameters:
        arrays - columns to add in DataFrame.
        Throws:
        UnsupportedTypeException - if array elements type is not Integer, Double or String
        EmptyArrayException
        ColumnSizeMismatch
